apps.localizedDescription:
This tweak makes Spotify think you have a Premium subscription, granting free listening and provides some additional features like custom lyrics.

These features are server sided and won't work:
• Very High audio quality
• Native playlist downloading
• Jam
• AI DJ/Playlist

To open Spotify links, use OpenSpotifySafariExtension. Remember to activate it and allow access in Settings > Safari > Extensions.
apps.name: EeveeSpotify
apps.subtitle: A tweak to get Spotify Premium for free

news.caption: Here I'll have some popular tweaked apps that are up to date, tested and high-quality. I'll try my best to update these apps at least once a month.
